headline: Leidos system installed to help improve efficiency and safety at Reagan National Airport
summary: Tower controllers and travelers at Washington, D.C.'s Reagan National Airport are expected to experience the benefits of a newly deployed Leidos (NYSE:LDOS) system designed to enhance both the efficiency and safety of flight operations.

headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks with Competitive Advantages and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
